0.1.name: wordpress/ip-blacklist-cloud
0.1.description:
IP Blacklist Cloud plugin allows you to blacklist IP addresses from visiting your WordPress website. Also, it submits your website link to the blocked IP database on http://ip-finder.me which gives the other users to view how many sites have blocked the specific IP and see their comments. New feature has been added to plugin which allows you to block usernames from spamming (comments) on your website.

Premium Software for managing multiple WordPress websites for synchronization: IP Blacklist Cloud Server - http://ip-finder.me/ipblc-server/
